All You - May 2014  USA

126 Pages | True PDF  | English | 30 MB 


ALL YOU magazine gives value-minded women like you the practical ideas they need for saving money and shopping smart in every area of life. Each issue features simple, crowd-pleasing recipes that use easy-to-find and inexpensive ingredients, affordable fashion for real women's bodies, and diet and fitness tips for busy women.
